{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-tsx","path":"/posts/21/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>You don't have to fight alone!</h2>\n<p>Now, a bigger new feature in a while: Allies!</p>\n<p>You can now buy allies to fight on your side, and they will also follow you along the map. Right now they only follow you, but I have planned to add some simple commands like \"stay here\" and \"follow me.\"</p>\n<p>They are not the brightest ones either, but can really make a difference in the early levels and are fun to watch flying around. You can also repair them in the build phase, so remember to do so if you have plans to use them. As always, there are three different level variants for them: green is the lowest, blue is the mid-tier, and red is the most advanced one.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/ac7a9/allies.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Allies\"\n        title=\"Allies\"\n        src=\"/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/64756/allies.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/a8a0d/allies.png 300w,\n/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/dface/allies.png 600w,\n/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/64756/allies.png 1200w,\n/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/28bdc/allies.png 1800w,\n/static/65d1941f70afe5b3e8d94b31425f4433/ac7a9/allies.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/ac7a9/allies-build.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Allies buildmenu\"\n        title=\"Allies buildmenu\"\n        src=\"/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/64756/allies-build.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/a8a0d/allies-build.png 300w,\n/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/dface/allies-build.png 600w,\n/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/64756/allies-build.png 1200w,\n/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/28bdc/allies-build.png 1800w,\n/static/82d6a3407634038d985b8e76fc04ed14/ac7a9/allies-build.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>HUD Updates</h2>\n<p>HUD/UI updates are now taking place, and the final layout is here! Some final touches in a few places and it is done.</p>\n<p>Here is the comparison to the old one:</p>\n<p>New:\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-rig