ld HUD\"\n        src=\"/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/64756/old-hud.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/a8a0d/old-hud.png 300w,\n/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/dface/old-hud.png 600w,\n/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/64756/old-hud.png 1200w,\n/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/28bdc/old-hud.png 1800w,\n/static/cf40cd78cf91f7f23c8fa74c38f63bff/ac7a9/old-hud.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The main menu now has a video rolling in the background. This is not the final version, but you get the idea.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/ac7a9/mainmenu.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Mainmenu\"\n        title=\"Mainmenu\"\n        src=\"/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/64756/mainmenu.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/a8a0d/mainmenu.png 300w,\n/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/dface/mainmenu.png 600w,\n/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/64756/mainmenu.png 1200w,\n/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/28bdc/mainmenu.png 1800w,\n/static/9224af56b97d41bc3e608334d65b6463/ac7a9/mainmenu.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>The beta demo is coming!</h2>\n<p>The beta demo is coming up nicely, but there is still a long list of bugs and issues to be fixed. So I'll continue with that and keep this post a bit short.\r\nAt the next Steam Next Fest, you should be able to play the beta demo, and I have to cut some other activities (like this blog) to get things ready.</p>\n<p>So next month, there will be no blog post. (Very likely, unless something miraculous happens and all the bugs will just be fixed by themselves.)\r\nAnd the planned release is still for this year, so soon it is time to wrap up everything.</p>\n<p>Stay tuned though! This has been a long road so far, and the finish line is on the horizon!</p>\n<p>Thanks again for joining me on this journey!</p>\n<p>See ya in October!</p>\n<p><em>Teemu, TheAspen</em></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"07.08.2025","title":"New HUD/UI and AI allies"}}},"pageContext":{"index":21}},"staticQueryHashes":["3359217925","3930925630"],"slicesMap":{}}